data.description: Move in ready! Convenient location close to shopping, schools and medical care! This house can be used in so many different ways. Large master bedroom with walk in closet.  Master can also be used as 2nd living area (with fireplace) and room for an office if needed.  Front living area can be used as formal dining. Numerous possibilities. Newer HVAC unit. Oversized back yard with privacy fence and large storage shed.  Refrigerator/washer/dryer stay.  Seller offering flooring allowance of $2500 to choose your new flooring or can be used towards closing costs with  agreed upon offer. Selling AS-IS.
